  FAMOUS PEOPLE
============================================================

Name:          Cleopatra VII
Lived:         69 - -30
Nationality:   Egyptian
Field:         Politics
Known For:     Last pharaoh of Egypt
Contribution:  Spoke 9 languages; allied with Caesar and Mark Antony; end of pharaonic era
Quote:         "I will not be triumphed over."

Name:          Isaac Newton
Lived:         1643 - 1727
Nationality:   English
Field:         Physics/Math
Known For:     Laws of Motion, Gravity
Contribution:  Principia Mathematica; invented calculus; explained planetary motion
Quote:         "If I have seen further, it is by standing on the shoulders of giants."

Name:          Mahatma Gandhi
Lived:         1869 - 1948
Nationality:   Indian
Field:         Politics
Known For:     Non-violent independence movement
Contribution:  Led India to independence; satyagraha philosophy; influenced MLK and Mandela
Quote:         "Be the change you wish to see in the world."

